SELECT [B.Categories].[BookId], [B.Categories].[CategoryId], [b.Category].[Id], [b.Category].[Description], [b.Category].[LastUpdate], [b.Category].[Name]
FROM [BookCategory] AS [B.Categories]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [b.Category] ON [B.Categories].[CategoryId] = [b.Category].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [B0].[Id]
        FROM [Books] AS [B0]
        INNER JOIN [Authors] AS [B.Author0] ON [B0].[AuthorId] = [B.Author0].[Id]
        WHERE EXISTS (
            SELECT 1
            FROM [BookCategory] AS [bc0]
            WHERE ([bc0].[CategoryId] = @__queryObj_CategoryId_Value_0) AND ([B0].[Id] = [bc0].[BookId]))
        ORDER BY [B0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [B.Categories].[BookId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[Id]
